  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        DISEASE CHARACTERISTICS:

          -  Histologically confirmed breast carcinoma

          -  Received first-line chemotherapy (in neoadjuvant or metastatic setting) comprising
             anthracyclines and/or taxanes, including for a second primary cancer

          -  Patient agrees to conservative surgery

          -  Hormone receptor status not specified

        PATIENT CHARACTERISTICS:

          -  Menopausal status not specified

          -  No contraindication for chemotherapy comprising anthracyclines and/or taxanes

        PRIOR CONCURRENT THERAPY:

          -  See Disease Characteristics

          -  No prior adjuvant therapy
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
